<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Privacy Policy • ReviewPilot</title>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body style="background: var(--bg); color: var(--text);">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main class="container section" style="max-width:900px;margin:32px auto;padding:0 22px;">
    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:42px;line-height:1.2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--muted)">We use essential cookies for session security and app functionality. With your consent, we may use analytics cookies to understand product usage.</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:20px">What we store</h2>
    <ul class="body-text" style="color:var(--muted)">
      <li>Account information you provide (name, email)</li>
      <li>Business settings (e.g., Google Place ID)</li>
      <li>Feedback submitted via public forms</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:20px">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--muted)">Click “Accept” in the cookie banner to store a small preference cookie (rp_cookie_ok=1) that hides the banner, and to allow optional analytics (if enabled).</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:20px">Contact</h2>
    <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--muted)">For questions or deletion requests, email support@reviewpilot.app</p>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

